{"tid":1693931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量] 石門深黃食店蒸廬拍烏蠅","createTime":"2019-11-05T01:18:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T13:57:29.000Z","uid":305022,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c33e24389c99e35dd903b97ec050e25b60a3f174","tid":1693931,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:19:00.000Z","msg":"本身諗住自己PO 啲相上黎，但係發現OPENRICE 介紹得幾好就麻煩大家click入去睇下喇:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E8%92%B8%E5%BB%AC-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-%E7%B2%B5%E8%8F%9C-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1-%E6%B9%AF%E5%93%81-r549305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openrice.com%2Fzh%2Fhongkong%2Fr-%25E8%2592%25B8%25E5%25BB%25AC-%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0-%25E7%25B2%25B5%25E8%258F%259C-%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%259D%25B1-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%2593%2581-r549305&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=69b35e1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.openrice.com/zh/hongkong/r-%E8%92%B8%E5%BB%AC-%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-%E7%B2%B5%E8%8F%9C-%E5%BB%A3%E6%9D%B1-%E6%B9%AF%E5%93%81-r549305</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ri0kX7U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRi0kX7U.jpg&h=8034da23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪面已經有各式認証，仲有非建制候選人海報，大家識做啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同一個商場仲有上車車仔面，入麵等黃店可以食，全部都好好味。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但因為呢間鋪係二樓，人流唔夠地鋪多，大家如果係附近番工或者假日不如去幫襯下。<br />\n<br />\n我都明白會有唔少人唔岩食車仔面, 同埋次次見到上車都排長龍會唔想排, 但上多兩層就有點心同蒸飯食!!!<br />\n<br />\n最重要係既係！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n入邊全部侍應都係年青絲打（老闆除外），全部清一色帶黑色口罩！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒撚黃打卡之選！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"703f20beb6396dbcb6376fee82f4a7d61f9201ca","tid":1693931,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801c433e06304c9ee997371317eeb904ef53b0a1","tid":1693931,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb8f43dd380c7d8cd1736e81adddb9b599ac67e","tid":1693931,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:21:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzexVA6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzexVA6.jpg&h=8cca900f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n返shift，射波齊參與<br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6d6274c05536163d63061f832d2234de5274c47","tid":1693931,"uid":130996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:22:17.000Z","msg":"雖然似打手post<br />\n都推下啦"},{"pid":"03b133bf0a27be80f4644c28759e9d0d097926f6","tid":1693931,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:27:08.000Z","msg":"唔係石門返工，試唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主不如介紹一下入面有咩蒸飯點心好食吖"},{"pid":"c368ba976341286764fffe80aa6da3a1c3b89ca7","tid":1693931,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse